TECH_PARAM_1.TECH_PARAM_MSG_LABEL: Date de début de cycle : JJ
TECH_PARAM_1.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: Date of the beginning of buoyancy reduction (relative to mission start day).

TECH_PARAM_2.TECH_PARAM_MSG_LABEL: Jour relatif de début de cycle.
TECH_PARAM_2.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: Day number of the beginning of buoyancy reduction (relative to mission start day).

TECH_PARAM_3.TECH_PARAM_MSG_LABEL: Heure de début cycle (nombre de minutes dans le jour courant). (BUOYANCY_REDUCTION_START_TIME).
TECH_PARAM_3.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: Date of the beginning of buoyancy reduction (relative to mission start day).

TECH_PARAM_4.TECH_PARAM_MSG_LABEL: Durée de l’activation forfaitaire de l’EV lors de la réduction d’émergence.
TECH_PARAM_4.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: Duration of the basic valve actions.

TECH_PARAM_5.TECH_PARAM_MSG_LABEL: Nombre de coups EV en surface.
TECH_PARAM_5.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: number of solenoid valve actions at the surface until the crossing of the GAP threshold

TECH_PARAM_6.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: is the float beached? - could be logical

TECH_PARAM_7.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: Number of minutes elapsed in the day at the beginning of the descent to parking depth.

TECH_PARAM_8.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: Number of minutes elapsed in the day when the float first stabilizes during descent to parking depth.

TECH_PARAM_9.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: Number of minutes elapsed in the day at the end of the descent to parking depth.

TECH_PARAM_10.TECH_PARAM_MSG_LABEL: Nombre de coups d'électrovanne en plongée vers Pdérive.
TECH_PARAM_10.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: number of valve actions between the crossing  of the gap threshold and the end of descent at park pressure

TECH_PARAM_11.TECH_PARAM_MSG_LABEL: Nombre de coups de pompe en plongée vers Pdérive.
TECH_PARAM_11.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: number of pump actions between the crossing  of the gap threshold and the end of descent at park pressure

TECH_PARAM_12.TECH_PARAM_MSG_LABEL: Date de début de dérive (JJ du mois seulement)
TECH_PARAM_12.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: time when park pressure is reached

TECH_PARAM_13.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: descent to park pressure: number of entries in margin around park pressure target - specifically, how many times the float enters the band of pressure surrounding the target park pressure (generally +/- 30db)

TECH_PARAM_14.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: number of times the float readjusts its buoyancy during park phase - using either the pump or EV

TECH_PARAM_15.TECH_PARAM_MSG_LABEL: Nombre de coups d'EV en dérive à Pdérive.
TECH_PARAM_15.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: number of valve actions during park phase

TECH_PARAM_16.TECH_PARAM_MSG_LABEL: Nombre de coups de pompe en dérive à Pdérive.
TECH_PARAM_16.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: number of pump actions while at park depth

TECH_PARAM_17.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: Number of minutes elapsed in the day at the beginning of the descent to profile depth.

TECH_PARAM_18.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: Number of minutes elapsed in the day at the end of the descent to profile depth.

TECH_PARAM_19.TECH_PARAM_MSG_LABEL: Nombre de coups EV descente profil.
TECH_PARAM_19.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: number of valve actions during descent to start profile pressure

TECH_PARAM_20.TECH_PARAM_MSG_LABEL: Nombre de coups de pompe descente profil.
TECH_PARAM_20.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: number of pump actions during descent to start profile pressure

TECH_PARAM_21.TECH_PARAM_MSG_LABEL: Nombre d'entrées consigne en dérive en attente profil.
TECH_PARAM_21.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: descent to profile pressure: number of entries in margin around profile pressure target  - specifically, how many times the float enters the band of pressure surrounding the target profile pressure (generally +/- 30db)

TECH_PARAM_22.TECH_PARAM_MSG_LABEL: Nombre de repositionnements en dérive en attente profil.
TECH_PARAM_22.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: at profile pressure stand-by, number of times the float readjusts its buoyancy - using either the pump or EV

TECH_PARAM_23.TECH_PARAM_MSG_LABEL: Nombre de coups EV en dérive en attente profil.
TECH_PARAM_23.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: number of valve actions while drifting at profile depth

TECH_PARAM_24.TECH_PARAM_MSG_LABEL: Nombre de coups de pompe en dérive en attente profil.
TECH_PARAM_24.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: Number of pump actions during drift at profile depth.

TECH_PARAM_25.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: Number of minutes elapsed in the day at the beginning of the ascent to the surface.

TECH_PARAM_26.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: time of the first transmission for this cycle

TECH_PARAM_27.TECH_PARAM_MSG_LABEL: Nombre de coups de pompe en remontée.
TECH_PARAM_27.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: number of pump actions between start and end of ascent

TECH_PARAM_28.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: Surface pressure recorded just before the previous descent but data is corrected on board the float. Note: cumulative NEGATIVE   offset  (real offset * -1) but no further correction required. Autocorrected

TECH_PARAM_31.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: real time clock status - 1= OK, 0=not OK

TECH_PARAM_32.TECH_PARAM_MSG_LABEL: Compteur de cohérence (nombre d’erreurs de la CTD).

TECH_PARAM_33.TECH_PARAM_MSG_LABEL: Etat du capteur DO (0 si OK, 1 sinon).
TECH_PARAM_33.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: Flag indicating the status of the Optode (see manual)

TECH_PARAM_34.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: Flag for GPS fix determination (1 if a valid fix has been transmitted in tech msg, 0 otherwise).

TECH_PARAM_35.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: the number of seconds required to obtain a GPS fix for a profile

TECH_PARAM_36.TECH_PARAM_MSG_LABEL: Nombre de relances effectuées lors de la session GPS.
TECH_PARAM_36.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: Number of times the GPS had to try to get a valid fix

TECH_PARAM_37.TECH_PARAM_MSG_LABEL: Nombre de télécommandes reçues (pour le cycle en cours).
TECH_PARAM_37.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: Number of remote control successfully considered.

TECH_PARAM_38.TECH_PARAM_MSG_LABEL: Nombre de télécommandes rejetées (pour le cycle en cours).
TECH_PARAM_38.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: Number of remote control rejected by the float (due to out of range value or remote control syntax error).

TECH_PARAM_39.TECH_PARAM_MSG_LABEL: Date de début de fin de vie: HH
TECH_PARAM_39.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: Clock time when End of Life mode starts

TECH_PARAM_40.TECH_PARAM_MSG_LABEL: Durée de la précédente session iridium.
TECH_PARAM_40.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: Duration on the previous Iridium session

TECH_PARAM_41.TECH_PARAM_MSG_LABEL: Nombre de SBD recus lors de la précédente session Iridium.
TECH_PARAM_41.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: Number of Incoming Iridium Messages Received during previous session

TECH_PARAM_42.TECH_PARAM_MSG_LABEL: Nombre de SBD émis lors de la précédente session Iridium.
TECH_PARAM_42.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: Number of Incoming Iridium Messages Sent during previous session

TECH_PARAM_43.TECH_PARAM_MSG_LABEL: Nombre de paquets de type 1 ou 8 - CTDO descente.
TECH_PARAM_43.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: Number of Iridium packets used to transmit sensor data collected during the descent phases (from surface to the parking depth and from the parking depth to the profile depth).

TECH_PARAM_44.TECH_PARAM_MSG_LABEL: Nombre de paquets de type 2 ou 9 - CTDO dérive.
TECH_PARAM_44.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: Number of Iridium packets used to transmit sensor data collected during the drift at park depth.

TECH_PARAM_45.TECH_PARAM_MSG_LABEL: Nombre de paquets de type 3 ou 10 - CTDO remontée.
TECH_PARAM_45.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: Number of Iridium packets used to transmit sensor data collected during the ascent from the profile depth to the surface.

TECH_PARAM_46.TECH_PARAM_MSG_LABEL: Nombre de tranches zone surface – descente.
TECH_PARAM_46.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: Descending profile reduction Number of slices in shallow zone - NTS

TECH_PARAM_47.TECH_PARAM_MSG_LABEL: Nombre de tranches zone fond - descente.
TECH_PARAM_47.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: Descending profile reduction Number of slices in deep zone - NTF

TECH_PARAM_48.TECH_PARAM_MSG_LABEL: Nombre de mesures en dérive à l’immersion de parking.

TECH_PARAM_49.TECH_PARAM_MSG_LABEL: Nombre de tranches zone surface – remontée.
TECH_PARAM_49.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: Ascending profile reduction Number of slices in shallow zone - NTS

TECH_PARAM_50.TECH_PARAM_MSG_LABEL: Nombre de tranches zone fond - remontée.
TECH_PARAM_50.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: Ascending profile reduction Number of slices in deep zone - NTF

TECH_PARAM_51.TECH_PARAM_MSG_LABEL: Pression du « point de subsurface » (dernier point de mesure « brut » pompé lors du profil ascendant)
TECH_PARAM_51.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: Last (shallowest) pumped raw pressure sample acquired during the ascent from the profile depth to the surface (i.e. just before the cut-off pressure where the pump is stopped) (in dbars).

TECH_PARAM_52.TECH_PARAM_MSG_LABEL: Nombre d'échouages détectés pendant le cycle.
TECH_PARAM_52.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: grounded flag , diagnostic bit - could also be logical?  Yes/no? 0/1? Or can be number of profiles during which the float grounded

TECH_PARAM_53.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: Day number when the float grounds for the first time (relative to mission start day).

TECH_PARAM_55.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: Phase of the float life or cycle when the first grounding occurred.  See the manual for phase definition - this will vary with float type

TECH_PARAM_56.TECH_PARAM_MSG_LABEL: Nombre d'ouvertures EV à pression constante pour déclarer le premier échouage.
TECH_PARAM_56.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: Number of valve actions done at constant pressure to set the grounded flag for the first grounding event

TECH_PARAM_57.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: Day number when the float grounds for the first time (relative to mission start day).

TECH_PARAM_59.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: Phase of the float life or cycle when the second grounding occurred.  See the manual for phase definition - this will vary with float type

TECH_PARAM_60.TECH_PARAM_MSG_LABEL: Nb d'ouvertures EV à pression constante pour déclarer l'échouage n°2
TECH_PARAM_60.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: Number of valve actions done at constant pressure to set the grounded flag for the second grounding event

TECH_PARAM_61.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: Number of Emergency ascents - Internal count

TECH_PARAM_62.TECH_PARAM_MSG_LABEL: Heure de la première remontée d'urgence.
TECH_PARAM_62.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: Number of minutes elapsed in the day of the float first emergency ascent.

TECH_PARAM_63.TECH_PARAM_MSG_LABEL: Pression de la première remontée d'urgence.
TECH_PARAM_63.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: Pressure that triggered the first emergency ascent

TECH_PARAM_64.TECH_PARAM_MSG_LABEL: Nombre de coups de pompe liés à la première remontée d’urgence.
TECH_PARAM_64.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: Emergency ascent - pump actions at emergency depth

TECH_PARAM_65.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: Day number of the float first emergency ascent (relative to mission start day).

TECH_PARAM_66.TECH_PARAM_MSG_LABEL: Nombre de coups de pompe avant décollage effectif quand grounded à la pression de profil.
TECH_PARAM_66.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: number of pump actions needed to leave the sea bottom when grounded at profile pressure

TECH_PARAM_67.TECH_PARAM_MSG_LABEL: Vitesse au moment du premier échouage.
TECH_PARAM_67.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: Vertical speed during the first grounding

TECH_PARAM_68.TECH_PARAM_MSG_LABEL: Vide interne au fond en début de remontée.
TECH_PARAM_68.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: Internal tube pressure [mbar] in profile depth

TECH_PARAM_69.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: Clock time of the last reset of the float

TECH_PARAM_70.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: Insulation voltage measured between 2 sub-parts of the float

TECH_PARAM_71.TECH_PARAM_MSG_LABEL: Number of descent CTD packets received
TECH_PARAM_71.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: Number of Iridium packets received to transmit sensor data collected during the descent phases (from surface to the parking depth and from the parking depth to the profile depth).

TECH_PARAM_72.TECH_PARAM_MSG_LABEL: Number of drift CTD packets received
TECH_PARAM_72.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: Number of Iridium packets received to transmit sensor data collected during the drift at park depth.

TECH_PARAM_73.TECH_PARAM_MSG_LABEL: Number of ascent CTD packets received
TECH_PARAM_73.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: Number of Iridium packets received to transmit sensor data collected during the ascent from the profile depth to the surface.

TECH_PARAM_74.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: Number of Iridium packets received to transmit hydraulic data recorded during the cycle.

TECH_PARAM_75.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: Number of times technical message #1 has been received.

TECH_PARAM_76.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: Number of times technical message #2 has been received.

TECH_PARAM_77.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: Number of times parameter message has been received.
